title: Howard Stern Is Wrong About Donald Trump Not Wanting To Win
text:
Howard Stern Is Wrong About Donald Trump Not Wanting To Win Radio talk show host makes preposterous claims regarding President Trump Infowars.com - February 4, 2017 Comments 
Alex Jones discusses false claims from radio host Howard Stern that Donald Trump never wanted to win the 2016 election. 
Stern’s comments fall apart given the fact that President Trump is following through on his campaign promises.
